"title": "7923: fellowship, in the gospel",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7923: fellowship, in the gospel",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A mutual participation in the blessings of God's grace. Believers are united with one another on the basis of their common reception of the benefits of salvation.</p>\n<h2>Fellowship and the community of God's people</h2>\n<h3>God calls out a community of people, for fellowship with himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:5–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:9–2:11</a></p>\n<h3>God will bless a people united in fellowship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:19-Matt18:20\">MAT 18:19–18:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:23-Jer31:25\">JER 31:23–31:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:29-1Cor11:34\">1CO 11:29–11:34</a> <em>Wrong relationships between God's people hinder the flow of his blessing.</em></p>\n<h3>God will restore fellowship with his scattered people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:12\">MIC 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:12-Isa11:13\">ISA 11:12–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:18\">JER 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:1\">JER 31:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:4-Jer50:5\">JER 50:4–50:5</a></p>\n<h2>Sharing in God's grace</h2>\n<h3>Fellowship in a common blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:4-Ps106:5\">PSA 106:4–106:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:32\">NUM 10:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:19\">JOS 22:19</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship in a common salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:23\">1CO 9:23</a> <em>sharing in the blessings of the gospel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7\">PHP 1:7</a> <em>sharing in God's grace</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:4\">TIT 1:4</a> <em>sharing a common faith</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1\">HEB 3:1</a> <em>sharing a common calling</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a> <em>sharing a common hope</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a> <em>sharing the divine nature</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:7\">1JN 1:7</a> <em>sharing in sanctification</em></p>\n<h3>Fellowship in a common inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship in God's family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:11\">HEB 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:9\">MAT 6:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:2\">LUK 11:2</a> <em>the family prayer in which believers together address God as Father</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:49-Matt12:50\">MAT 12:49–12:50</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:34-Mark3:35\">MRK 3:34–3:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:21\">LUK 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:8-Matt23:9\">MAT 23:8–23:9</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship between Jew and Gentile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">EPH 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17\">ROM 11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:27\">ROM 15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:16-Eph2:18\">EPH 2:16–2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Fellowship in holding a common truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:15\">2TH 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:63\">PSA 119:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:2\">1CO 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:2-1Cor15:3\">1CO 15:2–15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:2\">2TI 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14\">2TI 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:15\">TIT 2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Fellowship in union with Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:16-1Cor10:17\">1CO 10:16–10:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:19–2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:5\">ROM 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12\">1CO 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27\">1CO 12:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4-Eph4:5\">EPH 4:4–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>Fellowship through the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27-Ezek36:28\">EZK 36:27–36:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a></p>",
